<p>I could print the current version of the book right now and ship it. I have done so many times. It is 98% of what I want it to be when I do ship it in four months.</p>

<p>I have made everything else in the list except where noted. I have shipped things internationally from both America and Europe.</p>

<p>I grew up around small businesses of my parents and their friends, worked closely with entrepreneurs and read business books my whole life, and have done business consulting. I know double entry accounting, spreadsheets</p>

<p>The biggest risk is if the world ends before then. I donâ€™t think it will. Things will get hairy. Iâ€™ll find a way to fill your order just as</p>

<p>The worst case scenario is if hygienic darkroom retreating doesnâ€™t happen because people donâ€™t try. It is my function in life, so I am going to keep at it.</p>

